In the 80s DC put out a series called All-Star Squadron, based in 1941 when the JSA joined the war effort.  The war on the US homefront caused Roosevelt to create a team to defend its borders.  Originally the team consisted of Hawkman, Atom, Wildcat, and 3rd stringers like Robotman, Liberty Belle, Johnny Quick and a female Firebrand.  Evetually nearly every hero active during that time.  The series had such guests as Infinity Inc, the Freedom Fighters, and the Spectre.  

This pack includes the first 13 issues of the series, with the introduction of Firebrand, the Return of Robotman, and the reintroduction of Steel.
